# Project Overview

This is a web application built with [React](https://react.dev/) and [Vite](https://vitejs.dev/).

## Key Technologies

- **UI Framework**: [React](https://react.dev/)
- **Build Tool**: [Vite](https://vitejs.dev/)
- **Routing**: [@tanstack/react-router](https://tanstack.com/router)
- **Data Fetching**: [@tanstack/react-query](https://tanstack.com/query)
- **Forms**: [@tanstack/react-form](https://tanstack.com/form)
- **UI Components**: [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/)
- **Styling**: [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/)
- **Linting/Formatting**: [Biome](https://biomejs.dev/)

## Project Structure

- `src/main.tsx`: The application entry point.
- `src/routes`: Contains the route definitions for the application.
- `src/components`: Contains reusable React components.
  - `src/components/ui`: Contains `shadcn/ui` components.
- `src/lib`: Contains utility functions.
- `package.json`: Lists project dependencies and scripts.
